VALUES('DEVX-28', 'The mandatory trigger is not triggering even after the completion of all the signature reports', 'All the signature reports have been uploaded by the hotel side, but the mandatory trigger was not triggered automatically. In the Document Event, it is still showing as Processing, and the DocumentEventDetails collection indicates that some additional reports are waiting to be received. However, those are not signature reports. According to the observation, all of them are portal bulk reports.Below are the affected hotels with the 17th December business date.Test Demo 1Test Demo 2Test Demo 3', NULL, 'To Do', 'Medium', 'Bug', 'Portia Waduarachchi', 'Portia Waduarachchi', '{}', '{}', '2026-03-26 17:32:28.495', NULL, '2026-03-26 17:35:49.800', '[{"id": "10027", "body": "‘Report Demo 1’ report needs to be uploaded in order to trigger signature packets for Test Demo 1 hotel. Signature packs for Test Demo 2 and Test Demo 3 has already been sent.", "author": "Portia Waduarachchi", "created": "2026-03-26T17:35:49.800+0530", "updated": "2026-03-26T17:35:49.800+0530"}]'::jsonb, '{"id": "10027", "key": "DEVX-28", "self": "https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/6a02dde6-47b8-4c00-a42c-3bd078e9c043/rest/api/3/issue/10027", "expand": "renderedFields,names,schema,operations,editmeta,changelog,versionedRepresentations", "fields": {"labels": [], "status": {"id": "10000", "name": "To Do", "self": "https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/6a02dde6-47b8-4c00-a42c-3bd078e9c043/rest/api/3/status/10000", "iconUrl": "https://nwnhemantha.atlassian.net/images/icons/statuses/generic.png", "description": "", "statusCategory": {"id": 2, "key": "new", "name": "To Do", "self": "https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/6a02dde6-47b8-4c00-a42c-3bd078e9c043/rest/api/3/statuscategory/2", "colorName": "blue-gray"}}, "comment": {"self": "https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/6a02dde6-47b8-4c00-a42c-3bd078e9c043/rest/api/3/issue/10027/comment", "total": 1, "startAt": 0, "comments": [{"id": "10027", "body": {"ty